{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a3f8a0046c","title":"李先念在财贸系统革命造反联络委员会“打倒姚依林大会”上的讲话","origin":"国务院财贸系统革命造反联络委员会主办《财贸红旗》 1967年8月30日第9期第3版","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"da459f8c8a","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":21,"articleId":"a3f8a0046c"}],"tags":[{"id":"1ce2886aee","name":"姚依林","type":"人物"},{"id":"33f01f9c5a","name":"李先念","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"637e61c517","name":"李先念"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d0fcf9e53f","type":"title","text":"李先念在财贸系统革命造反联络委员会“打倒姚依林大会”上的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a3f8a0046c"},{"id":"33098958d7","type":"authors","text":"李先念","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a3f8a0046c"},{"id":"379bdc0a6d","type":"paragraph","text":"我坚决支持打倒姚依林大会的召开。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a3f8a0046c"},{"id":"4e236a0408","type":"paragraph","text":"我也是犯了错误的，以前你们炮轰李先念火烧李先念，大方向是正确的，就是打倒李先念方向也是正确的，因为我犯了错误嘛！希望同志们对我还要继续批评。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a3f8a0046c"},{"id":"bd4594b85d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理接见你们时，你们提出要停姚依林的职。姚依林的问题，我已向总理反映过了，总理同意你们的要求（口号）。现在我代表中央、总理宣布停止姚依林在国务院财贸办公室副主任、中共中央财贸政治部主任的职务。（呼口号）","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a3f8a0046c"},{"id":"9c02465a15","type":"paragraph","text":"我的错误，你们不要因为我而分两派，如果因为我分两派，我心里不安，感到惭愧。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a3f8a0046c"},{"id":"92c05d390b","type":"paragraph","text":"昨天总理接见你们，谈了抓革命促生产的问题，你们可以研究一下。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a3f8a0046c"},{"id":"62ecd021cd","type":"paragraph","text":"打倒刘邓陶！","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a3f8a0046c"},{"id":"98661babba","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的革命路线胜利万岁！","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a3f8a0046c"},{"id":"052667c930","type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的领袖毛主席万岁！","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a3f8a0046c"},{"id":"a80455f016","type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的毛泽东思想万岁！","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a3f8a0046c"}],"page":{"id":"0cb456da42","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a3f8a0046c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}